{"tid":546531,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"（少圖多字）關西//5日4夜 生日同回憶之旅","createTime":"2018-01-31T15:16:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T20:07:10.000Z","uid":150459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"03e5ba9026ee68653aa4ed174390ab4eb067c825","tid":546531,"uid":150459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T15:16:54.000Z","msg":"每年臨近生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都會去生日旅行<br />\n<br />\n以往幾年都有前任同我去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過佢早半年帽左我<br />\n<br />\n今年就⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n至於點解係回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過兩日先解話<br />\n<br />\n不過⋯點都好 旅行就一定要去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入正題 <br />\n5日4夜入面 <br />\n剩係玩大阪 奈良同埋京都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然仲有我每次都要去既環球影城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/225019_0d58e99b8f589b0ad20ea477409ee602.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F225019_0d58e99b8f589b0ad20ea477409ee602.png&h=e8b109fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝出門口真係好鬼大雨 又好鬼凍<br />\n<br />\n同埋求神拜佛左成個星期架UO唔好delay<br />\n真係準時飛同埋準時land<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係希望返黎都係咁 <br />\n<br />\n到左大阪都成2點 // 天氣真係好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/225333_2e5f5c9d16f6e359df14b081bf71809f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F225333_2e5f5c9d16f6e359df14b081bf71809f.png&h=15ffd150&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要上去JR ticket 到出返張IC卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起舊果張仲係前度到就傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/225719_655a2066fcd475ce716aaeb860d9b84e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F225719_655a2066fcd475ce716aaeb860d9b84e.png&h=687750a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟手上左架はるか<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好快就出左天王寺<br />\n仲快快手去民宿拎埋鑰匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/230028_d38f0d8edee5ff89177fbd5bc1f65e6d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F230028_d38f0d8edee5ff89177fbd5bc1f65e6d.png&h=ca68e3a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n四天王醬油拉麵<br />\n<br />\n有時候真係夜晚都發夢見到你 <br />\n對上一次係年幾前黎食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲要係同⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/31/230241_7d76d724d92b92afa96e64e93429c0f2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F31%2F230241_7d76d724d92b92afa96e64e93429c0f2.png&h=aaecec0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日真係無乜待別行程 <br />\n<br />\n周圍行左陣 相都無咩點影就去食埋晚餐返房休息<br />\n再加上辛苦命 <br />\n去旅行先黎病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我要休息⋯⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n聽日後日先係重點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n圖呢就聽日同後日會多好多掛⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n應該唔會爛尾掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"780b411748d07b5fa980c0655ee236c5d9047914","tid":546531,"uid":139100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-31T21:36:08.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n點解唔問佢攞返張卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebe96e9e8ee9fa094d1052b898fe88fbbb2e205","tid":546531,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T17:44:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d5177b15d98000593ab50e4b79f179e2c1906bd","tid":546531,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-06T20:07:10.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}